---
---

<section id="biografia" class="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-visual">
        <div class="about-image artist-portrait">
          <img src="/images/gisella-farinini.jpg" alt="Gisella Farinini - Pittrice" />
          <div class="image-caption">
            <span>Gisella Farinini</span>
            <span class="caption-note">Pittrice</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-label">L'Artista</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Biografia</h2>
        
        <div class="about-text">
          <!-- Coefficiente Artistico -->
          <div class="coefficient-badge">
            <div class="coefficient-value">5.6</div>
            <div class="coefficient-label">
              <span>Coefficiente Artistico</span>
              <span class="coefficient-sub">Assegnato dalla Critica d'Arte</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="intro">
            Mi chiamo Gisella e sin da piccola ho sempre desiderato divertirmi 
            con i colori e altri materiali.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Questo sito è una piccola vetrina di alcuni dei miei dipinti che sono 
            la traduzione del mio essere: <strong>un intreccio di esuberanza, 
            introversione, solitudine, irrequietezza, serenità, amore per il prossimo 
            e gioia di vivere</strong>, nonostante le forti asperità della vita.
          </p>
          
          <p>
            Dal <span class="highlight">1994</span>, anno della mia prima opera 
            "Occhio di Liguria", fino ad oggi, ho cercato di esprimere attraverso 
            la pittura le emozioni, i paesaggi e le sensazioni che la vita mi regala.
          </p>
          
          <div class="philosophy">
            <h3>Filosofia Artistica</h3>
            <div class="philosophy-grid">
              <div class="philosophy-item">
                <span class="letter">A</span>
                <div class="words">
                  <span>Amore</span>
                  <span>Armonia</span>
                  <span>Arricchimento</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="philosophy-item">
                <span class="letter">R</span>
                <div class="words">
                  <span>Reminiscenza</span>
                  <span>Radiosità</span>
                  <span>Rottura</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="philosophy-item">
                <span class="letter">T</span>
                <div class="words">
                  <span>Trasposizione</span>
                  <span>Trasformazione</span>
                  <span>Trasparenza</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="philosophy-item">
                <span class="letter">E</span>
                <div class="words">
                  <span>Ecletticità</span>
                  <span>Entusiasmo</span>
                  <span>Empatia</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 8rem 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-black) 0%, var(--color-black-light) 50%, var(--color-black) 100%);
  }
  
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;
    gap: 6rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .about-visual {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
  }
  
  .image-caption {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2rem;
    right: -2rem;
    background: var(--color-black-light);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    border-right: 3px solid var(--color-gold);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }
  
  .image-caption span:first-child {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
  }
  
  .caption-note {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .about-content {
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  
  .section-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .section-title {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  /* Coefficiente Artistico Badge */
  .coefficient-badge {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.15) 0%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.05) 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.4);
    border-left: 4px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .coefficient-badge::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.1) 50%, transparent 100%);
    animation: shimmer 3s infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes shimmer {
    0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
    100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
  }
  
  .coefficient-value {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    line-height: 1;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .coefficient-label {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  
  .coefficient-label span:first-child {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  
  .coefficient-sub {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  .about-text p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    font-weight: 300;
  }
  
  .about-text .intro {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-style: italic;
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  }
  
  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 400;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .philosophy {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(201, 169, 97, 0.2);
  }
  
  .philosophy h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
  }
  
  .philosophy-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .philosophy-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .letter {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    line-height: 1;
    opacity: 0.6;
  }
  
  .words {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .words span {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    font-style: italic;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 968px) {
    .about {
      padding: 4rem 0;
    }
    
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 4rem;
    }
    
    .about-content {
      padding-left: 0;
    }
    
    .image-caption {
      right: 0;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -1.5rem;
    }
    
    .philosophy-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    
    .coefficient-badge {
      padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .coefficient-value {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
    
    .coefficient-label span:first-child {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
